      "title_zh": "LinkedIn 招聘系统遭遇提示词注入攻击，暴露 AI 自动化招聘流程的安全脆弱性",
      "title_orig": "LinkedIn prompt injection shows how brittle AI recruiting has become - Startup Fortune",
